# Performance & Optimization

- Avoid O(n²) algorithms on large datasets—use hashing or streaming.  
- Defer heavy computations off the main thread or use pagination.  
- Cache repeated external calls or database queries.  
- Benchmark critical paths and log timings for future analysis.
